(1335, 160238, '2012-08-03 02:13:27', '"Calbindin-expressing cells in the other\nhippocampal layers [nonprincipal cell layers] were considered to be interneurons,\nalthough a few displaced principal cells may have been\nincluded. The number of calbindin-expressing cells outside\nthe principal cell layers was small (Table 2)."', 'p 558 right', 'data'),
