(1490, 160516, '2012-08-03 02:13:30', '"The dendrites [of the one labeled enkephalin-positive hippocampo-subicular cell] were immunonegative for PV [parvalbumin], CR [calretinin], VIP [vasoactive intestinal polypeptide], CCK [cholecystokinin], NK1 [neurokinin receptor 1], M2 [acetylcholine muscarinic receptor 2], and\nGABAA-a1 [gamma aminobutyric acid receptor A alpha 1 subunit] receptors."', 'p 10019 left bot', 'data'),
