(1496, 160519, '2012-08-03 02:13:30', '"Three targeted PV[parvalbumin]-positive cells were SM [somatostatin] negative,\nthereby excluding that they could be bistratified or oriens--lacunosum-moleculare cells (Klausberger and Somogyi, 2008).', 'p 10019 left top', 'data'),
