(1541, 160552, '2012-08-03 02:13:31', '"One neurone with characteristics resembling O-BiCs [oriens-bistratified]\nhas been recorded in the CA1 area and labelled in vivo and\nnamed ëtrilaminar interneuroneí (Sik et al. 1995).  The postsynaptic\ntargets of this cell were not evaluated quantitatively.  It remains to be tested if the O-BiCs reported here and the\nëtrilaminar interneuronesí comprise the same class of cells."', 'p 99 right mid', 'data'),
