(1565, 160568, '2012-08-03 02:13:31', '"In contrast to the CCK [cholecystokinin]+ MFAs [mossy fiber-associated cells] (see Fig. 6; see below), none of the CA3 RSBCs [regular-spiking basket cells] sent axon collaterals to\nthe hilus."', 'p 4243 right mid', 'data'),
