(1574, 160574, '2012-08-03 02:13:31', '"Furthermore, the majority of tested\nMFAs [mossy fiber-associated cells] were positive for CCK [cholecystokinin] (11 of 14\ncells), but PV [parvalbumin] and SOM [somatostatin] expressions were\nnever observed (0 of 3, and 0 of 8, respectively)."', 'p 4245 right mid', 'data');
