(1929, 161026, '2012-08-03 02:13:37', '"Somata double-labelled for VGLUT3 [vesicular glutamate transporter type 3] and CCK [cholecystokinin] were typically negative for CB [calbindin] (Fig. 4C and Table 2)."', 'p 557 right top', 'data'),
