(1941, 161034, '2012-08-03 02:13:37', '"None of the tested VGLUT3[vesicular glutamate transporter type 3]-positive neurons in the hippocampus [CA1, CA3, and dentate gyrus] (54 cells) and isocortex (20 cells) was immunoreactive for SS [somatostatin] (Fig. 7C)."', 'p 559 left bot', 'data'),
